descriptionHTML:
Shopping List & TO-DO notes

This handy app is used to manage the shopping items while shopping. Items can be toggled from shopping list to cart and vice versa . This app keeps the history of shopping list which would be helpful in analyzing the expense over the period of time.

TO-DO notes - Create a notes for shopping list and avoid worry of forgetting things.

Key Features -
- Wearable support with sync .
- Create as many shopping list as per your wish and track history of it in recent shopping list .
- Quickly add shopping items to the list .
- Handy toggling of shopping items from list to cart and vice versa .
- Create different shopping TO-DO notes .
- Easy to Access and Innovative .
- Good Usability .
- App Available for FREE to use .


For Advertisement / Query / Suggestions contact us at infonitydeveloper@gmail.com

#####################################################
Its been recommended to set Automatic updates on .

So that one can find how much he paid for groceries in a month/ year.  Thanks
